               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Jones's Defence.</hi> I was walking on, and this lad came and asked me the way to Poland-street—I directed him, and that is all I knew of him till I was taken.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Robinson's Defence.</hi> A few minutes after I left this young man the policeman came and collared me—I knew nothing of the robbery nor the other prisoner.</p>
